ActNational Defence Act
PrecisRe-appointment of VIHAR JOSHI of Ottawa, Ontario, as interim Chairperson of the Military Grievances External Review Committee, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of six months or until such time as a new Chairperson is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective December 16, 2023.
